{{Otheruses|Blackstar}}
The '''Blackstar Raiders''' were a widely feared and dangerous band of thugs and thieves who plundered dozens of backwater [[Outer Rim Territories/Legends|Outer Rim]] [[Planet/Legends|worlds]]. They were notorious for hitting weak and poorly-defended targets, and became widely targeted when [[Medara's Outpost]] hired a group of [[Mercenary/Legends|mercenaries]] to eliminate the Raiders.

